      "<p>It's been four months since we launched the &quot;new CACM.&quot; By                         now, I hope it is quite clear to our readers that the revamped                         flagship publication of ACM has undergone a rather dramatic                         transformation in both appearance and content. In my July                         editorial I began explaining the new editorial model of                         <i>Communications</i>, particularly the Research Highlights                         section that provides a bird's-eye view of the breadth and depth                         of computing research.</p>",
