      "<p>The current environment of information technology can be a                         complex place for analysts and firms to navigate, especially when                         making decisions about new product development, technology                         investment, and technology planning. Many industry analysts                         recognize that it is difficult, if not impossible, to accurately                         predict future technological advances.</p>",
